== Overview ==
The shrine was established in {{ill|531|ja|531st year|12=draft}} (25th year of {{ill|Emperor Keitai|ja|継体天皇|12=draft}}) to enshrine {{ill|Amatsuhikone|ja|天津日子根命|1=Amatsuhikone|12=draft}}.<ref name="gunshi">愛知縣額田郡誌、pp.353</ref>

